  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Retrospective study of all patients diagnosed with primary biliary cholangitis during January
      2001 to July 2016 at West China Hospital by review of medical records. The following
      variables will be retrospectively studied: age, sex, first symptoms, clinical
      characteristics, pathology, treatment, stage, complications of cirrhosis, other autoimmune
      diseases and long-term outcome.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
